title: Joey Diaz
itunes:title: Joey Diaz
description:
My HoneyDew this week is Joey Diaz! Joey joins me for part 3 of who knows how many parts! We get to age 18! He talks about the teenage years including his crazy step-father, practicing karate, working for the mob, and an exciting halloween party. Joey also talks in depth about finding his mother dead and how it affected him. It’s another great episode from the one and only Joey Diaz!
